metadata.name: Shadow Token
metadata.description: The Shadow token is the native token of Shadow Drive. Shadow Drive is the only decentralized data storage platform native to the Solana ecosystem that provides immutable decentralized permanent data storage without sacrificing performance. Files are uploaded to Shadow Drive using the Shdw Token. Shdw Tokens used to pay for file storage are burned and removed from supply. The Shdw Token has a fixed total supply and total supply decreases as Shadow Drive user adoption grows.

metadata.description: A collection born from the depths of darkness, Crimson Veins delves into the haunting beauty of life intertwined with entrapment. Each piece features twisted, vein-like roots that constrict around fragile figures, their cracked and glowing skin representing the fragility of existence. Surrounded by a pulsating, eerie void, the characters appear to be trapped in a nightmare, forever suspended between worlds. The limited color palette of red, black, and white accentuates the contrast, evoking a nightmarish, otherworldly aesthetic. This collection is a journey through the haunting edges of the subconscious, where beauty and fear coexist in disturbing harmony.
